column5: Hi all,  got the chance to swim with the stingrays on holiday, what an awesome experience!
There was a "stumpy" when I swam with them too in Bahamas.  They Said she was a bad girl that's how she ended up stumpy.    There cool , feel kinda like raw chicken on the underside.

There was a "stumpy" when I swam with them too in Bahamas. They Said she was a bad girl that's how she ended up stumpy. There cool , feel kinda like raw chicken on the underside.   LOL...yeah it does feel like a defrosted chicken breast!
Very cool. I did something similar in Curacao. They said they were like Pac-Man. They would eat anything that you put in front of them and wouldn't know when to stop.
